I Class: Singing. 2Canarese lessons:1 Barth's Histories of the Bible. Geogra-
phy of Palaestine, Arithmetic, Fractions. 2English lessons:1 Grammar. Spell-
ing tables. Translations from the English Bible and Marshman's history of
